OurVisionText: To be a national model with global expertise and a cornerstone in supporting the visions of Saudi Arabia and its aspirations toward leadership and digital excellence
OurMissionText: Create and develop an integrated, interactive, intelligent, and innovative technology environment that helps people accomplish their work easily, quickly and accurately
AboutTasheelText: Tasheel Information Technology (Tasheel) is one of the foremost IT solutions providers in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia for more than 30 years, primarily fulfilling the IT needs of government and private sectors in the areas of Information and Communication Technologies
rateUsText: Tasheel has a distinguished range of IT products and services that have been designed and built with the aim of contributing to the efficiency of services to the public and private sectors in Saudi Arabia and the Middle East region. Tasheel has helped government agencies automate their processes, address their business requirements, and achieve their IT and operational goals. As one of the pioneers of “true” e-government solutions, Tasheel has emerged as one of the top e-government solutions providers in the kingdom of Saudi Arabia
